---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import SectionLabel from "../../elements/SectionLabel.astro";
import CTAButton from "../../elements/CTAButton.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Project Alpha | Deployment Dossier"
  description="Project Alpha deployment dossier. A re/Human community architecture case study."
>
  <main class="main-wrapper relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto pt-32 pb-24 px-6">
      <!-- The Dossier Header -->
      <div class="border-b border-black/10 dark:border-white/10 pb-8 mb-16">
        <SectionLabel
          text="> MISSION_BRIEF // THE_CREATOR_MIGRATION"
          class="text-rh-ember!"
        />
        <h1
          class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter text-rh-ink dark:text-rh-chalk mt-4 mb-6"
        >
          ESCAPING THE ALGORITHM TRAP.
        </h1>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 max-w-sm">
          <div>
            <span
              class="font-mono text-[10px] text-rh-ink/40 dark:text-white/40 tracking-widest uppercase block mb-1"
              >INDUSTRY</span
            >
            <span class="font-mono text-sm text-rh-ink dark:text-rh-chalk"
              >Creator Economy</span
            >
          </div>
          <div>
            <span
              class="font-mono text-[10px] text-rh-ink/40 dark:text-white/40 tracking-widest uppercase block mb-1"
              >TIMEFRAME</span
            >
            <span class="font-mono text-sm text-rh-ink dark:text-rh-chalk"
              >60 Days</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- The Target Profile -->
      <div
        class="mb-16 p-8 border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10 bg-black/2 dark:bg-white/2 rounded-xl flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center"
      >
        <!-- Client Avatar/Logo -->
        <div
          class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-rh-ink border border-black/20 dark:border-white/20 overflow-hidden shrink-0 flex items-center justify-center grayscale contrast-125"
        >
          <span class="font-mono text-xs text-white/50">LOGO</span>
        </div>
        <!-- Credibility Baseline -->
        <div class="flex flex-col w-full">
          <span
            class="font-mono text-xs text-green-600 dark:text-green-400 mb-2 tracking-widest uppercase flex items-center"
          >
            <span
              class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-600 dark:bg-green-500 mr-2 animate-pulse"
            ></span>
            > TARGET_PROFILE // CREDENTIALS_VERIFIED
          </span>
          <h3
            class="text-2xl font-black text-rh-ink dark:text-white uppercase tracking-tight mb-2"
          >
            CLARK SELL / THAT
          </h3>
          <div
            class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10 font-mono text-xs text-rh-ink/70 dark:text-white/70 uppercase tracking-widest"
          >
            <span>[ BASELINE_ARR: $5M+ ]</span>
            <span>[ AUDIENCE: 1.2M ]</span>
            <span>[ PLATFORM: YOUTUBE/X ]</span>
            <span>[ STATUS: AUTHORITY ]</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Section 1: The Diagnostic -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <SectionLabel
          text="> SYS.DIAGNOSTIC // THE_BLEED"
          class="text-rh-ember! mb-6"
        />
        <p
          class="text-lg text-rh-ink/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6"
        >
          They had 150,000 followers across social media, a number that looked
          impressive on paper but translated to zero owned assets. Every piece
          of content was a rental payment to an algorithm they did not control.
          Their inbox was a warzone: 20+ hours per week fielding basic DMs,
          repeating the same answers, and chasing engagement metrics that reset
          to zero every morning.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-rh-ink/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          The business was highly profitable on the surface, but the founder was
          physically burning out. Revenue was directly coupled to their personal
          output. One week off meant a measurable dip in income. They were
          trapped on an exhausting content treadmill with no exit ramp, a
          classic case of a creator who had built a job, not a business.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Section 2: The Architecture -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <SectionLabel
          text="> SYS.EXECUTION // THE_BUILD"
          class="text-rh-ember! mb-6"
        />
        <p
          class="text-lg text-rh-ink/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6"
        >
          We deployed a private Skool environment and engineered a 4-week cohort
          onboarding loop designed to convert passive followers into active,
          paying community members. The onboarding sequence was built to run
          autonomously, with no founder involvement required after initial setup.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-rh-ink/70 dark:text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          We installed AI routing to handle basic support queries, eliminating
          roughly 80% of repetitive DM traffic. We then identified and trained 3
          'Super-Members' from within the existing audience to facilitate
          peer-to-peer coaching calls. The result was a self-sustaining
          ecosystem where value was generated by the community itself, not
          extracted from a single individual.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Section 3: The System Output (ROI Matrix) -->
      <section>
        <SectionLabel
          text="> SYS.OUTPUT // THE_TELEMETRY"
          class="text-rh-ember! mb-6"
        />
        <div
          class="grid grid-cols-2 border border-black/10 dark:border-white/10 divide-x divide-y divide-black/10 dark:divide-white/10 bg-rh-chalk dark:bg-rh-warm-dark rounded-xl overflow-hidden mt-12 mb-20"
        >
          <div class="p-6 flex flex-col">
            <span
              class="font-mono text-[10px] text-rh-ink/40 dark:text-white/40 mb-2 tracking-widest uppercase"
              >> METRIC_01 // NEW_MRR_ADDED</span
            >
            <span
              class="text-3xl font-black text-rh-ink dark:text-white uppercase tracking-tight"
              >$50K</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 flex flex-col">
            <span
              class="font-mono text-[10px] text-rh-ink/40 dark:text-white/40 mb-2 tracking-widest uppercase"
              >> METRIC_02 // FOUNDER_HOURS_SAVED</span
            >
            <span
              class="text-3xl font-black text-rh-ink dark:text-white uppercase tracking-tight"
              >15 HRS/WK</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 flex flex-col">
            <span
              class="font-mono text-[10px] text-rh-ink/40 dark:text-white/40 mb-2 tracking-widest uppercase"
              >> METRIC_03 // COHORT_COMPLETION</span
            >
            <span
              class="text-3xl font-black text-rh-ink dark:text-white uppercase tracking-tight"
              >85%</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 flex flex-col">
            <span
              class="font-mono text-[10px] text-rh-ink/40 dark:text-white/40 mb-2 tracking-widest uppercase"
              >> METRIC_04 // CULTURE_SCORE</span
            >
            <span
              class="text-3xl font-black text-rh-ink dark:text-white uppercase tracking-tight"
              >4.9/5</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- The Debrief Transcript -->
      <div class="mt-16 mb-20 border-l-2 border-rh-ember pl-8 py-2 relative">
        <SectionLabel
          text="> DEBRIEF_LOG // VERIFIED_AUDIO_TRANSCRIPT"
          class="text-rh-ember! mb-4"
        />
        <blockquote
          class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-rh-ink/90 dark:text-white/90 leading-relaxed font-medium mb-6"
        >
          "re/Human didn't just set up a Skool group for us. They fundamentally
          re-engineered how our audience interacts. We stepped out of the
          day-to-day community management, and our LTV tripled in 90 days. It is
          the most valuable asset in our business."
        </blockquote>
        <div
          class="font-mono text-sm text-rh-ink/50 dark:text-white/50 uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center gap-3"
        >
          <span class="w-8 h-px bg-black/20 dark:bg-white/20"></span> MATT GRAY,
          CEO
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- The Trap Door (Final CTA) -->
      <div
        class="mt-24 pt-16 border-t border-black/10 dark:border-white/10 flex flex-col items-center text-center"
      >
        <SectionLabel text="> END_OF_FILES // READY_TO_DEPLOY?" class="mb-6" />
        <h2
          class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter text-rh-ink dark:text-rh-chalk mb-10"
        >
          YOUR METRICS <span class="text-rh-ember">ARE NEXT.</span>
        </h2>
        <CTAButton href="/apply" variant="contrast">
          <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-rh-ember animate-pulse"></span>
          > APPLY_FOR_BUILD
        </CTAButton>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
